     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>The Epistle to the <hi>Reader.</hi>
   </head>
   <p>GEntle Readers, amongst all the cruell Strata<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>gems, poysonings and homicides, I haue here
described one, which in my iudgement pas<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>seth all that euer were inuented; together with Gods
prouidence in bringing it to light. And the sooner haue I penned it, that others may beware of
being deceiued by Sathan to doe the like, in hope it shall be concealed.</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>L. B.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
